the beard movement." This article is from

00:04:19.239 --> 00:04:24.229
the 1870s. This is his argument. "We have
come to the conclusion that the practice of

00:04:24.229 --> 00:04:29.699
shaving is alike ridiculous and absurd, and
that it violates one of the laws of nature.

00:04:29.699 --> 00:04:34.910
Now, our beard was not given us for no purpose;
that is evident. It was created for some wise

00:04:34.910 --> 00:04:39.740
purpose, and that was to keep the face and
throat warm, and thus be conducive to health.

00:04:39.740 --> 00:04:45.770
Let us look at a few facts. It has been calculated
that if one shaves three times a week, it

00:04:45.770 --> 00:04:48.740
grows twenty times as fast as if he did not
shave.

00:04:48.740 --> 00:04:52.240
Allowing two inches as the annual growth of
the beard, it will be seen that a man cuts

00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:58.120
off forty inches, or more than a yard of hair
a year, and the nutriment which supports this,

00:04:58.120 --> 00:05:02.530
and is thus wasted, might have gone to nourish
other parts of his body, and render him a

00:05:02.530 --> 00:05:04.349
healthy and handsome man."

00:05:04.349 --> 00:05:05.349
[laughter]

00:05:05.349 --> 00:05:08.800
"Again, allowing twenty minutes to each shaving
operation, three times a week, amounts to

00:05:08.800 --> 00:05:14.289
one hour a week, 52 hours a year. Supposing
a man to shave forty years, we find he has

00:05:14.289 --> 00:05:17.580
consumed about three months in the simple
act of shaving.

00:05:17.580 --> 00:05:22.350
And calculating the expense of each operation
at the small sum of six cents, we find it

00:05:22.350 --> 00:05:24.130
has cost him 360 dollars"

00:05:24.130 --> 00:05:25.130
[laughter]

00:05:25.130 --> 00:05:30.160
"In view of these facts, we cannot but regard
the practice of shaving as a decidedly barbarous

00:05:30.160 --> 00:05:35.250
one, and which ought to be discountenced by
the progressive civilization of the age."

00:05:35.250 --> 00:05:38.490
This is the sort of thing that shows up in
a newspaper back in the 1800s.

00:05:38.490 --> 00:05:43.500
Two things I want to point out to you. Number
one is "barbarous."

00:05:43.500 --> 00:05:44.630
[laughter]

00:05:44.630 --> 00:05:49.150
